oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Public gathering in Pulaski
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of people gathered outside the Pulaski courthouse. Men in military uniforms are lined on one side of the road. Spectators are gathered on both sides of the road, on the courthouse balconies, and the roof.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Courthouses; Military uniforms
